02:04:00.120 --> 02:04:03.320
in a very genuine, sincere way,

02:04:03.320 --> 02:04:08.320
it can leave one unraveled, uprooted, you know?

02:04:08.560 --> 02:04:10.320
It's not an easy thing to do.

02:04:10.320 --> 02:04:14.040
No wonder you see, it's like what Dostoevsky said,

02:04:14.040 --> 02:04:19.040
it seems that men with large hearts and deep minds

02:04:19.800 --> 02:04:22.160
seem to be the most miserable.

02:04:23.600 --> 02:04:25.520
And I think he says that in common punishment,

02:04:25.520 --> 02:04:27.320
I'm paraphrasing him.

